title: LARGE STUDIO IN ONE HOTEL SOBE RONEY!
posting_body: ['Large Studio with Direct Ocean View, overlooking The 1 Hotel pools!', 'The Roney Palace shares the building and amenities with 1 Hotel South Beach, one of Miami’s most luxurious resorts.', 'Life at the Roney Palace comes with three oceanfront swimming pools and beach service.', 'Additionally, the property boasts a rooftop swimming pool, bar and restaurant, as well as a variety of high-end and casual dining venues, including STK, Habitat and Plnthouse by Matthew Kenney.', 'Within the building you’ll find multiple fashion boutiques and fitness studios, including Soul Cycle and Anatomy Gym.', 'RENT include HD Cable, AC, Internet, Water, 1 Parking Space.', 'Walking distance to all restaurant South Beach has to offer from this stunning Oceanfront Luxury condo.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
